{"tid":1231493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔好俾柒婆陰到] 佢無話撤回！！！","createTime":"2019-06-16T12:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T13:18:50.000Z","uid":123933,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9008102ea43a3fe3f42946ae54477ebbc9a0b269","tid":1231493,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"1. 份新聞稿，只係話「停止」，無話撤回！<br />\n<br />\n2. 佢只係道歉，無話落台！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/16/P2019061600738.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201906%2F16%2FP2019061600738.htm&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=dee2883c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/16/P2019061600738.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，唔好再俾佢呃到！！！</span>"},{"pid":"6a621ea84fd915adb35406bb62e5cb4a2302c59c","tid":1231493,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:58:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5869414b4c6ac9de369afea587b8cc6494cb7f6e","tid":1231493,"uid":104834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"同意，必須撤回惡法，仲要收回暴動定性，無條件釋放所有被捕者"},{"pid":"453c587b64a4ae3e942c5f12be7e9c65e1ca908a","tid":1231493,"uid":123933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"緊急置頂呀！！！"},{"pid":"4a365cb4af516f08bd5ef36126a79e12289c855d","tid":1231493,"uid":123933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZjNouv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZjNouv.png&h=893e4750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">義士嘅遺願係一個都未有達到架！<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"2aebe316f9c359791b63969c2d96930f68a2b74c","tid":1231493,"uid":178933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:00:28.000Z","msg":"屌 不撤不散"},{"pid":"bc47fb25ba825fc929e23ea2eb10e6605b51b712","tid":1231493,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d467d006cfc5625351e668ee634910eb192c7f2","tid":1231493,"uid":41209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:02:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1bcfc07312f8b1594d9117ca73bcbeeea45bc4ff","tid":1231493,"uid":47647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61d20517b41b97ab67b8173d7e5ff6ad2f7127cc","tid":1231493,"uid":180999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb0c86e6b365725947987c70ecd4fcc8f1898b56","tid":1231493,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"不撤不散"},{"pid":"50f01f7af63638c03f80ad391635ef20ca1c5753","tid":1231493,"uid":205222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"200萬都係道歉<br />\n起碼要600萬先會放人+落台"},{"pid":"a5dab544462344ffaee8f0be9a2636fff08b50e5","tid":1231493,"uid":71024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQvs7Yb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQvs7Yb.png&h=50fd844e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《六月港殤奠禮需知》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人生自古誰無死， 留取丹心照汗青」<br />\n講出嚟好容易，做起嚟好撚難。<br />\n但一路走來，無數義士，前赴後繼為香港未來而犧牲。<br />\n命途多舛，尋晚更出現一位以死相諫嘅烈士。<br />\n<br />\n烈士絕不能枉死，我哋六十位大學生，<br />\n希望為您提供第一手陰間道路實況，提防牛鬼蛇神，<br />\n畀您喺外有蛇神，內有奸佞嘅環境，<br />\n好好安心立命，悼念死者。<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/juneforstfuneral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjuneforstfuneral&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=ed3f9648\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/juneforstfuneral</a><br />\n<br />\n面對自九號起幾何級倍增嘅白色恐怖，<br />\n及社會不斷傳來嘅噩耗。<br />\n有人灰心、悲傷、惶恐，但痛哭過後，<br />\n請您將所有淚水同悲痛，<br />\n化成對準政權嘅矛頭，用行動去傳承烈士嘅遺志。<br />\n<br />\n如果，您自問無「慷慨就義，捨身成仁」嘅勇氣；<br />\n亦請您堅持香港人獨有嘅骨氣。<br />\n<br />\n請大家懷憂壯志；<br />\n終點未至，未可中止。<br />\n自己香港，自己救。"},{"pid":"ffa3087135b2d08a5055d5e9380bed6e642ee728","tid":1231493,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T13:18:50.000Z","msg":"push"}]}